data.description: You do not want to miss this move-in ready 2-bedroom, 3-bath townhome in the desirable Highlands at Westbury neighborhood. The main floor features a spacious living room with large windows allowing for amazing natural light and opens up to the kitchen and dining area. The kitchen boasts wood cabinetry, ample storage space, and open concept living. Upstairs, the primary bedroom is accented by an en-suite bathroom along with a second bedroom and additional full bathroom. Residents enjoy access to exclusive amenities including the Clubhouse, Pool, Spa/Hot Tub, Tennis Courts, Park, and Playground. Easy access to I-25 makes commuting a breeze - just 30 minutes to downtown Denver or to Denver International Airport. Walk to Northwest Open Space and enjoy the views and walking paths or drive 5 minutes to the Ranch Country Club for a day of golf. Northglenn Marketplace and Thornton Town Center are both under ten minutes away allowing you to have the best of both worlds with convenience to TONS of shopping and dining options plus plenty of nearby outdoor activities. You will not want to miss the opportunity to see this home - call for your private showing today!
